#ChargeConj  anti-Sigma_c*-- Sigma(c)(2520)++
#ChargeConj  anti-Sigma_c*0 Sigma(c)(2520)0
#ChargeConj  anti-Xi_c*- Xi(c)(2645)+
#ChargeConj  anti-Xi_c*0 Xi(c)(2645)0

